Warning to all who care about sound quality: The 2Lions discs com from PAL sources, not NTSC. The frame rate is 25fps, not 24fps as it should be, so the audio is noticeably and annoyingly high pitched. My advice, avoid wasting your bandwidth on this file and find something from an NTSC source, provided they even bother to include the source info.
